data.description: This well-kept house sits on over a acre of land in town. Three bedrooms on the main level are matched by 3 nonconforming bedrooms in the lower level. The kitchen has been nicely updated. A huge deck adds an additional space to enjoy. Very quiet neighborhood with the high school and junior high are just a stone's throw away and the elementary school is but a short walk. Close to public swimming pool and a park.  Sale is subject to specific  purchase. Property has been identified.
